Package is.ru.tictactoe

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Board
    Board class contains functions regarding the board in tictactoe.
    Cell
    The Cell class gets and returns the char values for the sign in each cell.
    ComputerPlayer
    ComputerPlayer class inherits from Player class, to get current move (random) and the sign
    HumanPlayer
    HumanPlayer class inherits from Player class, to get current move and the sign
    Player
    Player class contains info of wins, losses and draws for a Player of the game Tic Tac Toe.
    Point
    The Point class contains information about the position of X and Y for the board
    TicTacToe
    The TicTacToe class is the brain of the application.
